{
  "stem": "1160.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he says-- he says-- he has it here that the 23 Jews in this farm has to be put against the wall on so and so date, and they have to be shot through the head.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] --the mayor said, well, if you can do something to save yourself, I won't know what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I won't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't tell me, and I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Something like this, he said.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what did the Jewish people do?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, the men, they were doing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They went up into the mountain-- went up on the mountain.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a lot of trees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It were like a forest, some parts.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they dug a-- a big hole, a deep hole.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It wasn't so wide, and it wasn't so long.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we were, you know-- it wasn't so comfortable there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it took a little while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they were working against time, so because the date was put out there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if the German promise that they will come, they will come.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So then we went into this.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We called it the bunker-- like a bunker-- a bunker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the raw earth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Raw earth, and we had a little-- about this wide, maybe-- for my mother and the four children.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this wide, and perhaps maybe this long for five of us to sit there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother got very sick with her stomach.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had some little food, which Mrs.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Smith gave before we went down there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She came upstairs, and she brought a little bit of flour.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she says, do what you want with it for the children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my mother did something-- I don't know-- little cookies-- I don't know-- with-- from nothing, you know-- with flour.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
